use https://docs.astral.sh/uv/reference/cli/

prioritize use of the ```uv ru``` command
prioritize use of the ```uv add``` commands when adding/installing dependencies
try and avoid uv pip commands in favor of uv primitive commands
use the uv tool command to run and manage --dev deps
use the uv to manage the package
use the uv to manage virtual environments
use the uv to run scripts
use the uv to add dependencies
in order to create requirements.txt use ```uv pip compile pyproject.toml -o requirements.txt```

use the uv to run python